---
import CategoryPage from '../components/pages/CategoryPage.astro';
---
<CategoryPage
  category="education"
  emoji="🎓"
  accent="#7c5fb8"
  accentSoft="#efe9f8"
  accentInk="#564189"
  eyebrow="Education"
  hero="The wrong school. The wrong degree. The dropout you don't talk about."
  lede="Years and money you can't get back. The class you failed twice. The thesis you never finished. The degree that taught you nothing useful."
  intro={[
    "Education was supposed to open doors. For a lot of people it just opened debt and a quiet sense of being behind everyone else.",
    "This page is for the dropouts, the wrong-major regretters, the people who went back at 32 and the people who never did. The bullied kid in the back row. The PhD that ate a decade.",
    "Learning is real. Schools are a system. The two are not the same thing, and figuring that out is sometimes its own painful education.",
  ]}
  prompt="What did school promise you that it didn't deliver?"
  metaTitle="Education failure stories — wrong school, dropout regret, the degree that didn't help"
  metaDescription="Real education failure stories: dropouts, wrong majors, degrees that led nowhere. Honest takes from people the brochures didn't mention."
/>
